{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/barrel.gif?t=1729318325\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Manage your own medieval tavern</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bartenders is a multiplayer tavern simulation game where you serve customers and build up your reputation. Prepare and serve your best dishes in a physics-based environment. Unlock new recipes and try to prepare the best dish in town. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/marketpazar.gif?t=1729318325\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Upgrade and advance</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy and upgrade furniture, equip better tools, and customize your tavern to your liking. Improve your tavern's decor to attract more customers and start to serve to the upper class. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/ZamanaKarsi.gif?t=1729318325\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play with your friends or hire to boost your servicing capacity</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with up to 10 friends together, and hire NPCs to share the workload.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/extras/DayAndNight.gif?t=1729318325\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Day and night cycle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Open your tavern at night, interact with the village, and upgrade your tavern during the day.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729318325","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass